source.name: 2007 Veterans Employability Research Survey
source.description: The 2007 Veterans Employability Research Survey (VERS) was conducted to determine the factors that impact veterans' employability resulting from participation in the VR&E Program. The study consists of a nationally representative survey of veterans who have applied to the VR&E Program, but who discontinued the program at various points as well as a comparison group of veterans who have completed the program.
